To check if your computer can communicate with the connected Android device/emulator:

adb reverse tcp:8081 tcp:8081

Error if no devices/emulators found: like this
  erro - adb.exe: error: no devices/emulators found

If ADB is recognizing your device/emulator, you can proceed to run the app:
for android
npx react-native run-android
for ios 
npx react-native run-ios


After successfully building the project, start the Metro Bundler:

npm start


